Package: metricsutils
Title: Utilities For Cleaning, Transforming, And Analyzing Venture Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sarah", "Masri", , "sarah.masri@creativedestructionlab.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a set of utilities for cleaning, transforming, and analyzing structured data, with a focus on standardizing inconsistent inputs, parsing complex fields, and generating reliable, analysis-ready datasets. It includes tools for handling messy text, extracting and formatting numeric and financial values, reshaping data, and creating summary metrics, enabling efficient and reproducible data workflows.
